## 流程

1. 初始化弹性配置 ConfigElasticity
```plain
config = ConfigElasticity(pre_config, config_buffer, scenario.scenario_buffer)
```

2. 初始化弹性对象 Elasticity
```plain
fluid = Elasticity(config.fluid_max_part_num[None], pre_config, config)
```
所有都 fill(0)
3. 初始化弹性场景
```plain
init_elasticity_scenario(ngrid, fluid, bound, config)  # todo
```
* 初始化pos0，R旋转矩阵初始化成单位矩阵
```plain
init_values(fluid)
```
* 初始化邻域：邻居搜索
```plain
obj.neighbors_initial[i, obj.neighbors_num[i]] = neighb_pid
obj.neighbors_num[i] += 1
```
* 计算校正矩阵L
```plain
elasticity_compute_L(fluid, fluid, config) 
```

3. 求解弹性
```plain
elasticity_step(fluid, config)
```
![图片](data:image/png;base64,)

(1) 计算右边

```plain
elasticity_compute_rotations(fluid, fluid, config)
elasticity_compute_stress(fluid, fluid, config)
elasticity_compute_force(fluid, fluid, config)
elasticity_compute_rhs(fluid, config)  
```

(2) 共轭梯度迭代

```plain
elasticity_iter_vel_adv(fluid, fluid, config) 
```
* 初始化迭代：残差r、向量p、中间速度vel_adv
```plain
elasticity_iter_init(i, obj)
```
* 计算矩阵向量积Ap
```plain
elasticity_iter_Ap(i, obj, nobj, config)
```
* 主要迭代过程，得到弹性影响的中间速度vel_adv
```plain
elasticity_iter_update_p(i, obj)
```

(3) 更新弹性加速度

```plain
SPH_advection_elasticity_acc(fluid, config)
```
